"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\"}, {\"begin\": 244, \"end\": 249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"score\": 0.9993510527845006, \"rank\": 0.0005868666011911921, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Powered byOutside SANTIAGO\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 26}, {\"ngram\": \"CHILE - OCTOBER\", \"from\": 28, \"to\": 43}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 107, \"to\": 117}, {\"ngram\": \"Track Cycling - Men's Madison\", \"from\": 121, \"to\": 150}, {\"ngram\": \"Parque Pe\\u00f1alolen\", \"from\": 154, \"to\": 170}, {\"ngram\": \"Day\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 177}, {\"ngram\": \"Santiago\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 191}, {\"ngram\": \"October\", \"from\": 213, \"to\": 220}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Photo by Buda Mendes/Getty Images)(Photo: Buda Mendes/Getty Images) If there is one thing you must know aboutGrant Koontzit's that he really loves cycling.\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(Photo\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 257}, {\"ngram\": \"Buda Mendes/Getty Images)(Photo\", \"from\": 261, \"to\": 292}, {\"ngram\": \"Buda Mendes/Getty Images\", \"from\": 294, \"to\": 318}, {\"ngram\": \"one thing\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 341}, {\"ngram\": \"aboutGrant Koontzit\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 375}, {\"ngram\": \"cycling\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That singular fact, or relationship if you consider it in a slightly different context, explains a lot.\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 512, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That singular fact\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 427}, {\"ngram\": \"relationship\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 444}, {\"ngram\": \"a slightly different context\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 495}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a love story that has brought him from the road, to gravel, to the track, as a journeyman looking for a career to make the love story last just a little bit longer.\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 685, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a love story\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 533}, {\"ngram\": \"the road\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 593}, {\"ngram\": \"a journeyman\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 610}, {\"ngram\": \"a career\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 631}, {\"ngram\": \"the love story\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 654}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's taken him from nightly dinners of eggs and sweet potatoes in a pop-up RV parked illegally on the streets of Boulder, to a bikepacking trip to theMidsouth gravel raceon the eve of the COVID-19 pandemic, and then, pivotally, to the Eurovision-esque glitz and pageantry of the made-for-TV Track Champions League.\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 1000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 761, \"end\": 763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Recreational_vehicle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9261026697183375e-14, \"text\": \"RV\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Recreational_vehicle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Recreational_vehicle\"}, {\"begin\": 799, \"end\": 806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boulder\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.124755004131735e-28, \"text\": \"Boulder\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boulder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boulder\"}, {\"begin\": 874, \"end\": 891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"score\": 0.9999997446216511, \"rank\": 2.5537042711353275e-07, \"text\": \"COVID-19 pandemic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nightly dinners\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 721}, {\"ngram\": \"eggs\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 729}, {\"ngram\": \"sweet potatoes\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 795}, {\"ngram\": \"a bikepacking trip\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 829}, {\"ngram\": \"the eve\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eurovision-esque glitz\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 943}, {\"ngram\": \"pageantry\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"TV\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ultimately that passion has delivered the 30-year-old to theParis Olympicsas Team USA's sole male track representative, even if it has been a wildly roundabout way to get there.\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1079, \"end\": 1087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.7125302164815673, \"rank\": 0.2549044583732913, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that passion\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1025}, {\"ngram\": \"a wildly roundabout way\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1165}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In a sense, I was a lost puppy,\\\" Koontz said a couple of days before the Games began of his journey from gravel vagabond to the Olympic prep camp in Belgium.\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1339, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1331, \"end\": 1338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9986891980526338, \"rank\": 0.001043102537319288, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sense\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1192}, {\"ngram\": \"a lost puppy\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1212}, {\"ngram\": \"Koontz\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"a couple\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1235}, {\"ngram\": \"days\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1243}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"his journey\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1281}, {\"ngram\": \"gravel vagabond\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1302}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic prep camp\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Three years ago I was watching the Olympics from the sideline as the track world today shut down during the pandemic.\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"the sideline\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1402}, {\"ngram\": \"the track world\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1421}, {\"ngram\": \"the pandemic\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was still very much a novice.\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1490, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a novice\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1489}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew I had the barebones tools to be a good track racer but I had not had a chance to excel.\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1585, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the barebones tools\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1523}, {\"ngram\": \"a good track racer\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1548}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously, I wanted to make it to Paris but I needed to start out taking baby steps forward.\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1622, \"end\": 1627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.83440119919256e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"baby steps\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1671}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I guess that's always been the paralyzing thing for me, just the distractions elsewhere.\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1769, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the paralyzing thing\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1728}, {\"ngram\": \"just the distractions\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1758}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Things like gravel became a distraction because it was really about having fun and staying motivated through the pandemic, but I knew, and my wife really convinced me, that if I could get to focus on one thing I would be super good at it.\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 2008, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Things\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1776}, {\"ngram\": \"gravel\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1788}, {\"ngram\": \"a distraction\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1809}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1848}, {\"ngram\": \"staying\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 1860}, {\"ngram\": \"the pandemic\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1891}, {\"ngram\": \"my wife\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1916}, {\"ngram\": \"one thing\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 1979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I was finally able to do that and be good enough to turn my back on other interesting opportunities was what brought me success.\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2144, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my back\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2080}, {\"ngram\": \"other interesting opportunities\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2115}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The focus had to be falling in love with the process and not only relying on the love of cycling that has been going on for 12 years.\\\"\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2279, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The focus\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2180}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2197}, {\"ngram\": \"the love\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2230}, {\"ngram\": \"cycling\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2241}, {\"ngram\": \"12 years\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2277}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While those sentiments and the journey Koontz has been on do fit the beats of other athletes' dragged-out battles against luck, competition, and motivation to make it to the Olympic level, Koontz had the added challenge that comes from the United States' complicated relationship with track cycling.\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2580, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2521, \"end\": 2534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.998208158358381, \"rank\": 0.001521292191230938, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those sentiments\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2303}, {\"ngram\": \"the journey\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2319}, {\"ngram\": \"Koontz\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2326}, {\"ngram\": \"the beats\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2355}, {\"ngram\": \"other athletes' dragged-out battles\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2394}, {\"ngram\": \"luck\", \"from\": 2403, \"to\": 2407}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2420}, {\"ngram\": \"motivation\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2436}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic level\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2468}, {\"ngram\": \"Koontz\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2476}, {\"ngram\": \"the added challenge\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2500}, {\"ngram\": \"track cycling\", \"from\": 2566, \"to\": 2579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the early 1900s, track cycling in the United States was huge.\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2623, \"end\": 2636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.998208158358381, \"rank\": 0.001521292191230938, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the early 1900s\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2600}, {\"ngram\": \"track cycling\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2615}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Figures likeMajor Taylorwere international stars, while fans packed famous venues like Madison Square Garden in New York City to watch not basketball or hockey, but track events.\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2825, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2759, \"end\": 2772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.584511980762209e-16, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Figures likeMajor Taylorwere international stars\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2695}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2707}, {\"ngram\": \"famous venues\", \"from\": 2715, \"to\": 2728}, {\"ngram\": \"Madison Square Garden\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2755}, {\"ngram\": \"not basketball\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2796}, {\"ngram\": \"hockey\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2806}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, throughout the first half of the 20th century European professionals came to the United States to race track events for extra cash and exposure.\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2979, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2916, \"end\": 2929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.998208158358381, \"rank\": 0.001521292191230938, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2833}, {\"ngram\": \"the first half\", \"from\": 2846, \"to\": 2860}, {\"ngram\": \"the 20th century\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2880}, {\"ngram\": \"European professionals\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 2903}, {\"ngram\": \"track events\", \"from\": 2938, \"to\": 2950}, {\"ngram\": \"extra cash\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 2965}, {\"ngram\": \"exposure\", \"from\": 2970, \"to\": 2978}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, track cycling is but a shadow of its past.\", \"from\": 2981, \"to\": 3028, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"track cycling\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 2999}, {\"ngram\": \"a shadow\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3015}, {\"ngram\": \"its past\", \"from\": 3019, \"to\": 3027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Velodromes are sparse, with only three indoor tracks among the 22 total tracks currently in use in the U.S., which puts the U.S. on the back foot in international competition and development.\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3220, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Velodromes\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3039}, {\"ngram\": \"only three indoor tracks\", \"from\": 3057, \"to\": 3081}, {\"ngram\": \"the 22 total tracks\", \"from\": 3088, \"to\": 3107}, {\"ngram\": \"use\", \"from\": 3121, \"to\": 3124}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 3128, \"to\": 3136}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 3149, \"to\": 3157}, {\"ngram\": \"the back foot\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3174}, {\"ngram\": \"international competition\", \"from\": 3178, \"to\": 3203}, {\"ngram\": \"development\", \"from\": 3208, \"to\": 3219}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There have been exceptions to the rule - most notablyJennifer Valente's gold medal at the omnium in the Tokyo Olympics and the women's team pursuit silver medals in London and Rio, bronze in Tokyo, and nowgold in Paris- but on the men's side, success in major championships has been below par as evidenced by their inability to qualify a team pursuit for the past two Olympic cycles despite significant investment into that cause.\", \"from\": 3222, \"to\": 3652, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3387, \"end\": 3393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.999999993302481, \"rank\": 6.097526386592697e-09, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 3398, \"end\": 3401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9997829531529335, \"rank\": 0.0002170939668418972, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 3413, \"end\": 3418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9781741171491986, \"rank\": 0.02230862483111465, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"exceptions\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3248}, {\"ngram\": \"the rule\", \"from\": 3252, \"to\": 3260}, {\"ngram\": \"most notablyJennifer\", \"from\": 3263, \"to\": 3283}, {\"ngram\": \"Valente's gold medal\", \"from\": 3284, \"to\": 3304}, {\"ngram\": \"the omnium\", \"from\": 3308, \"to\": 3318}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 3322, \"to\": 3340}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's team\", \"from\": 3345, \"to\": 3361}, {\"ngram\": \"silver medals\", \"from\": 3370, \"to\": 3383}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 3403, \"to\": 3409}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris-\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3441}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's side\", \"from\": 3449, \"to\": 3463}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 3465, \"to\": 3472}, {\"ngram\": \"major championships\", \"from\": 3476, \"to\": 3495}, {\"ngram\": \"par\", \"from\": 3511, \"to\": 3514}, {\"ngram\": \"their inability\", \"from\": 3531, \"to\": 3546}, {\"ngram\": \"a team pursuit\", \"from\": 3558, \"to\": 3572}, {\"ngram\": \"the past two Olympic cycles\", \"from\": 3577, \"to\": 3604}, {\"ngram\": \"significant investment\", \"from\": 3613, \"to\": 3635}, {\"ngram\": \"that cause\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3651}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have shifted my focus a few times,\\\" Koontz said of his time in the Olympic pipeline with USA Cycling's track program.\", \"from\": 3654, \"to\": 3774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3746, \"end\": 3757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Cycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4605671958388335e-31, \"text\": \"USA Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Cycling\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my focus\", \"from\": 3670, \"to\": 3678}, {\"ngram\": \"Koontz\", \"from\": 3693, \"to\": 3699}, {\"ngram\": \"his time\", \"from\": 3708, \"to\": 3716}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic pipeline\", \"from\": 3720, \"to\": 3740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The initial plan was for us to qualify in the team pursuit, but once it was clear that the writing was on the wall that we were not going to qualify for the team pursuit I switched my focus to the Madison which is what I thought we'd have a better chance of getting a spot.\", \"from\": 3775, \"to\": 4049, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3973, \"end\": 3980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Madison\", \"score\": 0.9999999953606675, \"rank\": 4.639186052986415e-09, \"text\": \"Madison\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Madison\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Madison\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The initial plan\", \"from\": 3776, \"to\": 3792}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3801, \"to\": 3803}, {\"ngram\": \"the team pursuit\", \"from\": 3818, \"to\": 3834}, {\"ngram\": \"the writing\", \"from\": 3863, \"to\": 3874}, {\"ngram\": \"the wall\", \"from\": 3882, \"to\": 3890}, {\"ngram\": \"the team pursuit\", \"from\": 3929, \"to\": 3945}, {\"ngram\": \"my focus\", \"from\": 3957, \"to\": 3965}, {\"ngram\": \"a better chance\", \"from\": 4015, \"to\": 4030}, {\"ngram\": \"a spot\", \"from\": 4042, \"to\": 4048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I honestly had not focused a lot on the omnium until this year because I thought my best shot at the Olympics was in literally any other event.\", \"from\": 4051, \"to\": 4195, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the omnium\", \"from\": 4088, \"to\": 4098}, {\"ngram\": \"this year\", \"from\": 4105, \"to\": 4114}, {\"ngram\": \"my best shot\", \"from\": 4133, \"to\": 4145}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4149, \"to\": 4161}, {\"ngram\": \"any other event\", \"from\": 4179, \"to\": 4194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But ultimately my focus on all the other events has helped me be a well-rounded rider for the omnium.\\\"\", \"from\": 4196, \"to\": 4298, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my focus\", \"from\": 4211, \"to\": 4219}, {\"ngram\": \"all the other events\", \"from\": 4223, \"to\": 4243}, {\"ngram\": \"a well-rounded rider\", \"from\": 4261, \"to\": 4281}, {\"ngram\": \"the omnium\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4296}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nevertheless, qualifying questions, funding concerns, and the uncertainty of selection are now behind Koontz.\", \"from\": 4300, \"to\": 4409, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"qualifying questions\", \"from\": 4314, \"to\": 4334}, {\"ngram\": \"funding concerns\", \"from\": 4336, \"to\": 4352}, {\"ngram\": \"the uncertainty\", \"from\": 4358, \"to\": 4373}, {\"ngram\": \"selection\", \"from\": 4377, \"to\": 4386}, {\"ngram\": \"Koontz\", \"from\": 4402, \"to\": 4408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, he is now facing the purity of the racing and faces the ultimate test of endurance track racers: the omnium.\", \"from\": 4410, \"to\": 4527, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the purity\", \"from\": 4436, \"to\": 4446}, {\"ngram\": \"the racing\", \"from\": 4450, \"to\": 4460}, {\"ngram\": \"the ultimate test\", \"from\": 4471, \"to\": 4488}, {\"ngram\": \"endurance track racers\", \"from\": 4492, \"to\": 4514}, {\"ngram\": \"the omnium\", \"from\": 4516, \"to\": 4526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The omnium is a one-day event consisting of four races: a scratch race, a tempo race, an eliminator, and the all-important points race.\", \"from\": 4529, \"to\": 4664, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The omnium\", \"from\": 4529, \"to\": 4539}, {\"ngram\": \"a one-day event\", \"from\": 4543, \"to\": 4558}, {\"ngram\": \"four races\", \"from\": 4573, \"to\": 4583}, {\"ngram\": \"a scratch race\", \"from\": 4585, \"to\": 4599}, {\"ngram\": \"a tempo race\", \"from\": 4601, \"to\": 4613}, {\"ngram\": \"an eliminator\", \"from\": 4615, \"to\": 4628}, {\"ngram\": \"the all-important points race\", \"from\": 4634, \"to\": 4663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While each of these races has its own intricacies, when it comes down to brass-tax the demands of the races are similar to the technical challenges the rest of cycling faces.\", \"from\": 4665, \"to\": 4839, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these races\", \"from\": 4679, \"to\": 4690}, {\"ngram\": \"its own intricacies\", \"from\": 4695, \"to\": 4714}, {\"ngram\": \"brass-tax\", \"from\": 4738, \"to\": 4747}, {\"ngram\": \"the demands\", \"from\": 4748, \"to\": 4759}, {\"ngram\": \"the races\", \"from\": 4763, \"to\": 4772}, {\"ngram\": \"the technical challenges\", \"from\": 4788, \"to\": 4812}, {\"ngram\": \"cycling faces\", \"from\": 4825, \"to\": 4838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More and more, the big variable beyond raw watts is the aerodynamics of the rider.\", \"from\": 4840, \"to\": 4922, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the big variable\", \"from\": 4855, \"to\": 4871}, {\"ngram\": \"raw watts\", \"from\": 4879, \"to\": 4888}, {\"ngram\": \"the aerodynamics\", \"from\": 4892, \"to\": 4908}, {\"ngram\": \"the rider\", \"from\": 4912, \"to\": 4921}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Koontz, a self-described cycling romantic, the technical challenges might not seem like they would be of much interest.\", \"from\": 4924, \"to\": 5047, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Koontz\", \"from\": 4928, \"to\": 4934}, {\"ngram\": \"the technical challenges\", \"from\": 4971, \"to\": 4995}, {\"ngram\": \"much interest\", \"from\": 5033, \"to\": 5046}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But ever since he was selected to the team earlier this summer Koontz has delved into the tech challenges that come with racing at the tippy-top of cycling performance.\", \"from\": 5048, \"to\": 5216, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 5082, \"to\": 5090}, {\"ngram\": \"Koontz\", \"from\": 5111, \"to\": 5117}, {\"ngram\": \"the tech challenges\", \"from\": 5134, \"to\": 5153}, {\"ngram\": \"racing\", \"from\": 5169, \"to\": 5175}, {\"ngram\": \"the tippy-top\", \"from\": 5179, \"to\": 5192}, {\"ngram\": \"cycling performance\", \"from\": 5196, \"to\": 5215}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Two weeks ago I did a bunch of on-bike on-track testing,\\\" Koontz said.\", \"from\": 5218, \"to\": 5289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bunch\", \"from\": 5239, \"to\": 5246}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 5261, \"to\": 5266}, {\"ngram\": \"Koontz\", \"from\": 5277, \"to\": 5283}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously, that means everything has to be taken with a grain of salt because outside forces can affect it, but still it is pivotal to see what helmet to use, what gloves to use, what shoe covers to use - everything.\\\"\", \"from\": 5290, \"to\": 5508, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 5313, \"to\": 5323}, {\"ngram\": \"a grain\", \"from\": 5345, \"to\": 5352}, {\"ngram\": \"salt\", \"from\": 5356, \"to\": 5360}, {\"ngram\": \"outside forces\", \"from\": 5369, \"to\": 5383}, {\"ngram\": \"what helmet\", \"from\": 5430, \"to\": 5441}, {\"ngram\": \"shoe\", \"from\": 5475, \"to\": 5479}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 5496, \"to\": 5506}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With eyes towards optimizing everything, hard choices had to be made, including skipping over a bike built for the American track program with the express purpose of having an advantage at these Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 5510, \"to\": 5720, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5625, \"end\": 5633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999139358843, \"rank\": 7.060754492093302e-08, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"eyes\", \"from\": 5515, \"to\": 5519}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 5539, \"to\": 5549}, {\"ngram\": \"hard choices\", \"from\": 5551, \"to\": 5563}, {\"ngram\": \"a bike\", \"from\": 5604, \"to\": 5610}, {\"ngram\": \"the express purpose\", \"from\": 5653, \"to\": 5672}, {\"ngram\": \"an advantage\", \"from\": 5683, \"to\": 5695}, {\"ngram\": \"these Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 5699, \"to\": 5719}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Look just released a new P24 track bikeand it just did not work for me,\\\" Koontz said.\", \"from\": 5722, \"to\": 5808, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new P24 track bikeand\", \"from\": 5742, \"to\": 5765}, {\"ngram\": \"Koontz\", \"from\": 5796, \"to\": 5802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is not adjustable enough for me and my position so we went back to the (Look) T20 bike because, at the end of the day, the bike is only as good as your position.\", \"from\": 5809, \"to\": 5974, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the (Look) T20 bike\", \"from\": 5880, \"to\": 5899}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 5912, \"to\": 5919}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 5923, \"to\": 5930}, {\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 5932, \"to\": 5940}, {\"ngram\": \"your position\", \"from\": 5960, \"to\": 5973}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can save way more on helmets and shoe covers and those things rather than just riding all the cool new shit.\\\"\", \"from\": 5975, \"to\": 6088, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"helmets\", \"from\": 6000, \"to\": 6007}, {\"ngram\": \"shoe covers\", \"from\": 6012, \"to\": 6023}, {\"ngram\": \"those things\", \"from\": 6028, \"to\": 6040}, {\"ngram\": \"all the cool new shit\", \"from\": 6065, \"to\": 6086}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet on August 8, the deck gets reset again.\", \"from\": 6090, \"to\": 6133, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 6097, \"to\": 6103}, {\"ngram\": \"the deck\", \"from\": 6107, \"to\": 6115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All the riders from around the world who will compete for medals over the frantic four events will have to forget about the aero advantages they may or may not have and simply race.\", \"from\": 6134, \"to\": 6315, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All the riders\", \"from\": 6134, \"to\": 6148}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 6161, \"to\": 6170}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 6192, \"to\": 6198}, {\"ngram\": \"the frantic four events\", \"from\": 6204, \"to\": 6227}, {\"ngram\": \"the aero advantages\", \"from\": 6254, \"to\": 6273}, {\"ngram\": \"simply race\", \"from\": 6303, \"to\": 6314}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the end of the day, whatever way one splices it, racing is always more of an art than it is a science.\", \"from\": 6316, \"to\": 6421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 6319, \"to\": 6326}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 6330, \"to\": 6337}, {\"ngram\": \"racing\", \"from\": 6368, \"to\": 6374}, {\"ngram\": \"an art\", \"from\": 6393, \"to\": 6399}, {\"ngram\": \"a science\", \"from\": 6411, \"to\": 6420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The omnium is no different, especially since its biggest point haul comes in the race where surprises can turn up the established order.\", \"from\": 6422, \"to\": 6558, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The omnium\", \"from\": 6422, \"to\": 6432}, {\"ngram\": \"its biggest point haul\", \"from\": 6467, \"to\": 6489}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 6499, \"to\": 6507}, {\"ngram\": \"surprises\", \"from\": 6514, \"to\": 6523}, {\"ngram\": \"the established order\", \"from\": 6536, \"to\": 6557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Consistency is key,\\\" Koontz said.\", \"from\": 6560, \"to\": 6594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Consistency\", \"from\": 6561, \"to\": 6572}, {\"ngram\": \"Koontz\", \"from\": 6582, \"to\": 6588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You do not have to be the best in the world at all of the events, it's just about consistency over the first three races and just placing in the money, because the points race is the highest weighted event for those overall points, and that's really what the training has been geared towards.\", \"from\": 6595, \"to\": 6888, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 6630, \"to\": 6639}, {\"ngram\": \"the events\", \"from\": 6650, \"to\": 6660}, {\"ngram\": \"consistency\", \"from\": 6678, \"to\": 6689}, {\"ngram\": \"the first three races\", \"from\": 6695, \"to\": 6716}, {\"ngram\": \"the money\", \"from\": 6737, \"to\": 6746}, {\"ngram\": \"the points race\", \"from\": 6756, \"to\": 6771}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest weighted event\", \"from\": 6775, \"to\": 6801}, {\"ngram\": \"those overall points\", \"from\": 6806, \"to\": 6826}, {\"ngram\": \"the training\", \"from\": 6851, \"to\": 6863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you can not points race, you can not be the omnium winner.\\\"\", \"from\": 6889, \"to\": 6951, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"race\", \"from\": 6911, \"to\": 6915}, {\"ngram\": \"the omnium winner\", \"from\": 6932, \"to\": 6949}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To learn more about Koontz and his journey, be sure to check out hisInstagram (@rakoooontz) where he has been sharing details and journal entries from the pivotal points over the last few years.\", \"from\": 6953, \"to\": 7147, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Koontz\", \"from\": 6973, \"to\": 6979}, {\"ngram\": \"his journey\", \"from\": 6984, \"to\": 6995}, {\"ngram\": \"hisInstagram\", \"from\": 7018, \"to\": 7030}, {\"ngram\": \"@rakoooontz\", \"from\": 7032, \"to\": 7043}, {\"ngram\": \"details\", \"from\": 7071, \"to\": 7078}, {\"ngram\": \"journal entries\", \"from\": 7083, \"to\": 7098}, {\"ngram\": \"the pivotal points\", \"from\": 7104, \"to\": 7122}, {\"ngram\": \"the last few years\", \"from\": 7128, \"to\": 7146}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is well worth the read!\", \"from\": 7148, \"to\": 7174, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}]}"